comments.body:
[~alice]: Yep, after key pair creation the test sequence tries to navigate to the images landing page but fails since Firefox seems stuck on the create/download key pair step.  When I tested locally the Firefox download window/button seems highlighted, and the browser seems to defer to the OS to take control of the UI for the file download operation.  Bizarre, since we've seem to properly set the Firefox profile options in...

{code}
ffprofile.set_preference("browser.helperApps.neverAsk.saveToDisk", "application/x-pem-file, text/csv, application/xml, text/plain, image/jpeg, application/x-apple-diskimage, application/zip")
{code}
